Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week to SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total time between SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week and SW-AE Assign Reviewers
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-Reviewer Agreed after the execution of SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Time from SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week to SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 3 days'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week and SW-Reviewer Selection is now due
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is now due'

Name: Average time it takes SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week to be followed by a reviewer response (e.g., SW-Reviewer Agreed, SW-Reviewer Declined, or SW-Reviewer No Response)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Total resolution time of SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week measured until the first occurrence of SW-Reviewer Agreed
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Agreed'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week and SW-Reviewer Declined
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Declined'

Name: Time from SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week to SW-Awaiting EIC Decision in variants that include both activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Awaiting EIC Decision'

Name: Average time between SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week and SW-Reviewer Unavailable
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Unavailable'

Name: Total time from SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week to the next reminder activity (Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1 or Reviewer Invitation Reminder 2)
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'Reviewer Invitation Reminder 1'

Name: Minimum time it takes SW-AE Assign Reviewers after the execution of SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-AE Assign Reviewers'

Name: Time of SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week measured as the interval between its timestamp and the timestamp of the preceding SW-Initial Reviewer Selection
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Initial Reviewer Selection' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week'

Name: Average time from SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week to SW-Reviewer Selection is 3 days late in high-duration variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is 3 days late'

Name: Elapsed time between SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week and Assign a Different Editor in complex reassignment variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'Assign a Different Editor'

Name: Total time until SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week is performed after Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation' and activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week'

Name: Time from SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week to SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation in variants where AE recommendation is eventually reached
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-Awaiting AE Recommendation'

Name: Average time it takes the process to reach SW-EIC Major Revision after SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-EIC Major Revision'

Name: Minimum time between SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week and the final decision activity (e.g., SW-EIC Accept, SW-EIC Reject, or SW-EIC Reject & Resubmit) in completed cases
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'SW-Reviewer Selection is due in 1 week' and activity 'SW-EIC Accept'
